
===============================================================================
=                                    USAGE                                    =
===============================================================================

Return (to_life); is the Ionis Official Students Portal.

Requirement
===========

* PHP >= 5.3
* libssh2-php
* Web Server
* MySQL

Initialization
==============

1) Create a MySQL database.
2) Get the latest version of Ionis-Users-Informations (SQL version) :
   https://github.com/db0company/Ionis-Users-Informations
3) Edit the "conf.php" file.

===============================================================================
=                                 DEVELOPMENT                                 =
===============================================================================

Coding Style
============

* Variables names
  Objects attributes : theVariableName, blue, protocolName
  Internal function variables : like Objects attributes
  Global variables : categ_name (def_include_dir)
  Objects methods : like objects attributes
  Objects getters/setters : getTheVariableName, setProtocolName, isBlue (boolean)
  Global function names : can_you_sleep
  Filenames : include/tools.php, src/Portal.class.php (objects)

* Align functions names :
  private function	hello($arg)


Files & Directories
====================

* include
  general includes, countaining global functions, global variable

* view
  echo html

* src
  objects


Informations
============

* include/def.php contain directories definitions

